node.text:
one of my favorite things to do in new york is just sit and observe the street style.. everyone from the trendy soho girls to the badass grandmas who’ve lived here their entire lives. so here’s the first episode of a little series about what new yorkers are wearing :)
//
shot by the lovely jenn roberts
edited + produced by yours truly
and of course a huge thank you to everyone who appeared in this video, please be super kind to them in the comments <3
//
also i hadn’t heard of her before, but according to y’all in the comments, @karenbritchick does a similar series so check her out if you want!
